# 13/04/2003 - [hisham] Ok, now I am almost sure that Shared linking works.
# 09/04/2003 - [rafasgj] Fixed bug: executables were not being "strip"-ed.
#            - Removed linkprogs. Now all files are linked using
#              link_directory and Link_Or_Expand. Old linkprogs substituted
#              for strip_and_link.
#            - Fixed bug that was adding "*" broken links in $HOME.
#            - [detsch] Fixed Shared linking.
# 06/04/2003 - [rafasgj] Changed linkdir to Link_Or_Expand. Still missing
#              "Settings" and "Executables"
